snippet.title: Vail VR - Official Meta Quest 2 Alpha Announce Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Watch the announcement trailer for Vail VR's Quest 2 Alpha, arriving in Summer 2023. See the competitive multiplayer shooter in action in this exciting teaser. The Quest 2 Alpha will feature new maps, modes, weapons, and every major update so far. Participants can also get their hands on exclusive in-game cosmetics.

#SummerOfGaming
